title: Happy Birthday, Taylor Swift!
description:
Today is the holiday every Swiftie should be celebrating! Happy birthday to our queen, Taylor Swift! We discuss what she has accomplished, what she predicted for herself in the last decade, and the fun way that Ana and Lacey got to celebrate her birthTAY!
And don't forget to listen tomorrow when we announce our winners the autographed albums!
Thank you so much for listening! Let us know what you would like to hear from us! There are lots of ways to reach us!
